
<html>
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <title>注册验证码</title>
    <style>
      body {
        font-family:
          "Helvetica Neue", Helvetica, Arial, "PingFang SC", "Hiragino Sans GB",
          "Microsoft YaHei", sans-serif;
        background: #f7f7f7;
        color: #333;
        padding: 32px;
      }
      .container {
        background: #fff;
        border-radius: 8px;
        max-width: 480px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 32px 24px;
        box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.06);
      }
      .code {
        font-size: 2em;
        letter-spacing: 8px;
        color: #1677ff;
        font-weight: bold;
        margin: 24px 0;
      }
      .footer {
        margin-top: 32px;
        font-size: 0.95em;
        color: #888;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <h2>欢迎注册{{appName}}！</h2>
      <p>您的注册验证码为：</p>
      <div class="code">{{code}}</div>
      <p>请在 <b>{{expireMinutes}}</b> 分钟内输入验证码完成注册。</p>
      <p>如果您未发起此请求，请忽略此邮件。</p>
      <div class="footer">
        <p>—— {{appName}} 团队</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>